data.description: 2 HOMES on 5.56 Acres with possibility of a third, a huge shop, several storage buildings, and a tiny home!  BOTH HOMES ARE 3 BEDROOMS WITH 2 BATHS each.   The 2012 Barndominium is 2382 sq feet and the other home is 1852 sq feet. 5 mins from I-40!  The land is so beautiful and peaceful and with minimal updates and finishes, the large Barndiminium would make a great home while working on the main house.   The Barndominium includes 3 beds, 2 baths and an office. It needs some doors, flooring, baseboards, and a good cleaning.  Everything mechanical is working and the bones appear great. The other home needs a lot of work. The roof leaks and sheetrock damage is present on the ceiling.  Electrical works in part of the house, but not all.  Foundation appears good. Please ask your agent to text me for more pictures if interested.  The garage next to the main house has been converted into a church and is a great flex space with several possibilities. Buyer to verify all info.
